        <content type="html" xml:base="https://blog.jimmac.eu/posts/klatovy/">&lt;p&gt;They say you can&#x27;t forget how to ride a bicycle. Well I don&#x27;t think it applies to FPV racing. Haven&#x27;t touched the sticks in a year. But that does not make me not hang out with old buddies at the longest running event in Czechia.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
